WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.664
Next, choose the agent harness CTO should run.

2
00:00:02.664 --> 00:00:11.293
A harness coordinates the normal agent workflow, then helps route work across providers based on model fit, availability, and your remaining balance.

3
00:00:11.293 --> 00:00:17.084
OpenClaw and Hermes provide the same CTO harness role, so choose the one you want CTO to coordinate.
